data.description: **The sellers currently have a VA loan that could be assumed. Their current interest rate is 4.25%!**  Here's a great opportunity in Poquoson! This 1900 5 bedroom colonial style home is waiting for vision and restoration. New A/C! Newly refininshed LR and DR floors! There are so many reasons that residents love being part of the "Bull Island" community! It's in close proximity to major employment sites including military bases, NASA, and Huntington Ingalls Shipyard. In addition, Poquoson is reported to have a very low crime rate and the Poquoson School System has consistently ranked among the best in the state. Call/text/email today for an in person or video showing!
